{"tid":333800,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做過3年雜誌編輯，你問我答","createTime":"2017-07-24T07:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T01:57:38.000Z","uid":125208,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a94df4f918c4db3c2137d9a978a38cd6d3af424","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"主要做漫畫、玩具稿<br />\n隨便問，有機會自爆既問題除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacfc5e9ab5dff5c0f414caeb8beea28e7acb345","tid":333800,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:37:53.000Z","msg":"辛唔辛苦"},{"pid":"8aa9c8d71517fcc5a9e8ca6062c8b6e76c7d2b10","tid":333800,"uid":20014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:39:37.000Z","msg":"幾錢個月？<br />\n<br />\n通常幾點收工？"},{"pid":"33023ccf3455ef98c771e1921eba42ff1900e8f4","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辛唔辛苦</blockquote><br />\n截稿嗰幾日可以忙到小哂老母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b37cdb3f5f5400f11a4e2c3a1dfc794b3c11d0","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢個月？<br />\n<br />\n通常幾點收工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人工偏低，而且新入職要預左俾人壓價，我走時13k有找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常收6點幾，但從來唔會準時走"},{"pid":"6cf6e7e5fa7886ef1fc91f8fa47e9511e76bf950","tid":333800,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"係邊間做"},{"pid":"94060f1efe3dc8de346f182ab6e26dbb31e322b0","tid":333800,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>辛唔辛苦</blockquote><br />\n截稿嗰幾日可以忙到小哂老母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n周刊/月刊？"},{"pid":"c92990eeede7e8f89c4417d2dc07bedbcc470f3e","tid":333800,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係邊間做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你叫佢自爆？"},{"pid":"fa668b51888fc6f20289a7ab22aabf89a4bd3579","tid":333800,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:55:56.000Z","msg":"有乜潛規矩"},{"pid":"2965ffe6eb7658e6e784b248a5045f95e568c160","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係邊間做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自爆，不了"},{"pid":"62cec5cca2436b5a362befbe5a3fabd036d0fe5d","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>辛唔辛苦</blockquote><br />\n截稿嗰幾日可以忙到小哂老母咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n周刊/月刊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有自爆傾向，算係周啦"},{"pid":"225a0c317044ac10307ce994c3a2a7423f910ea0","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有乜潛規矩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔算做過好多份工，有冇類似例子可以俾我諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ceef74c7c0b55ad0b93a6bbc44edaccb40992f0","tid":333800,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"易入行嗎？ 好想入行但冇乜空缺"},{"pid":"e62b82be0c1cb2301099924e0fb9466ea98e83cf","tid":333800,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有乜潛規矩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔算做過好多份工，有冇類似例子可以俾我諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如有冇發夢見過一啲灰色地帶"},{"pid":"f0e283d12a6467738341fcd00eb59d95ba3a891a","tid":333800,"uid":17322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:05:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5d1c318e8c36261cb3e1c6f4ec492515c898b1c","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>易入行嗎？ 好想入行但冇乜空缺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的確係好少，但你睇下而家出版業咩時勢，都估到會係咁，加上算係舒服既工種，所以即使冇前途，好多人做耐左都唔會走<br />\n如果做過相關實習會易d"},{"pid":"f8a87a0d6c08f8f6f00dab13cd9ee6d6c09d5b64","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有乜潛規矩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔算做過好多份工，有冇類似例子可以俾我諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如有冇發夢見過一啲灰色地帶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發夢見過如果經常寄信去抽獎，中過2、3次之後，你中獎機會就會急跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5683e5a548d7750aad14bc3c5b768bfb30914a1b","tid":333800,"uid":86898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:21:10.000Z","msg":"係唔係有回佣/玩具/禮物收<br />\n然後有把聲：篇稿寫得好好睇睇"},{"pid":"a20a30d9509e209887957aec9a8bf4dfdbc619e6","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多唔多人送野俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPS4呀SWITCH呀個D大把啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想，但其實未有過呢d sponsor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n暴龍機呢啲過氣倉底貨就有機會大家分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fff3cd16e092945682976bc701fe2ee73820d82","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係唔係有回佣/玩具/禮物收<br />\n然後有把聲：篇稿寫得好好睇睇</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n有就有，不過係會送俾讀者"},{"pid":"baa5a473d3bcfd256161879cd4968d990f29524f","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係唔係有回佣/玩具/禮物收<br />\n然後有把聲：篇稿寫得好好睇睇</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n有就有，不過係會送俾讀者</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n送唔晒就擺倉等下期，過晒氣先機會自己拎"},{"pid":"5d05be4cf29c41a97d9f7ac365443b5ea0d4fbf8","tid":333800,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"而家做緊咩？"},{"pid":"a3d93b7034c62ac9dc633f706472e4acaa8e1288","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家做緊咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n19 admin妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d886125620e0d813329b16a5abaae7de83f352c","tid":333800,"uid":516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>易入行嗎？ 好想入行但冇乜空缺</blockquote><br />\nGame書一本執一本仲做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ae2db43555c0cc37e9a99cad1b12e1efecdbba","tid":333800,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>易入行嗎？ 好想入行但冇乜空缺</blockquote><br />\nGame書一本執一本仲做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候重去做print media既的確係搵黎搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非真係興趣&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;搵錢"}]}